{"tid":1357832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"義士宣言：不排除成立臨時立法會","createTime":"2019-07-23T20:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T03:33:44.000Z","uid":268978,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b412a1177fa874f0590a99a3ce53a4627cb5375","tid":1357832,"uid":268978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T20:38:18.000Z","msg":"唔係好覺有人post片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=4c8fa42f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a><br />\n<br />\n包圍中聯辦的示威者在傍晚 7 時許宣讀宣言，重申民間五大訴求，又表示不排除會成立臨時立法會，捍衛香港民主。<br />\n<br />\n示威者在宣言中自稱是一群香港市民，表示自 6 月初以來，數以百萬計香港人以和平非暴力方式向政府表達「反送中」的訴求，事件其後更<span style=\"color: blue;\">令五名香港人犧牲、以死相諫</span>，期望喚醒政府的良知，可惜只換來冷漠的回應，<span style=\"color: red;\">完全無視市民訴求</span>，政府更<span style=\"color: red;\">放任警察以暴力對付市民</span>。宣言指政府選擇與民為敵，重申<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求包括：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 撤回逃犯條例修訂；<br />\n2. 終止一切對被捕示威者的法律程序；<br />\n3. 撤回 6.12「暴動」定義；<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會調查警察；<br />\n5. 以行政命令即時解散立法會及實現雙普選。</span><br />\n<br />\n發表宣言的示威者表示，不願意見到再有香港人犧牲，又稱會以一切方法迫使政府回應。又指控自主權回歸後，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">政府惡法不斷，不排除成立臨時立法會，以捍衛香港的民主。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSource: 立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/7-21-包圍中聯辦-示威者門外發宣言-不排除成立臨時立法會/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F7-21-%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E9%96%80%E5%A4%96%E7%99%BC%E5%AE%A3%E8%A8%80-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%2F&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdUxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=e6ff5fd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F7-21-%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E9%96%80%E5%A4%96%E7%99%BC%E5%AE%A3%E8%A8%80-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%2F&h=e611641f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/7-21-包圍中聯辦-示威者門外發宣言-不排除成立臨時立法會/</a>"},{"pid":"10846508ade1807287bd61c3eff3794cf797a5ed","tid":1357832,"uid":233873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e22f45b97f4b761abc5bdf24e919568984ede14d","tid":1357832,"uid":189934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}